---
title: Homestyle Chorizo Filo Pie with Roasted Potato & Leek
description: Roast veggies, leek and chorizo sounds like a dangerously good combination. There’s only one way to contain this much deliciousness, bake it together underneath a golden filo pastry to transform this trio of flavour into one irresistible pie.
